Package com.medilabo.microfront.service

Class NoteService

java.lang.Object
com.medilabo.microfront.service.NoteService
@Service public class NoteService extends Object
Service class for managing notes and interacting with external services using WebClient. Provides methods to fetch, update, validate, and delete notes, as well as to find notes for a patient

      public List<NoteBean> fetchNotesByPatientId(String token, Long patientId)
      Fetches a list of notes associated with a given patient ID.
      Parameters:
      token - Authorization token for the request.
      patientId - The ID of the patient whose notes are being fetched.
      Returns:
      List of NoteBean objects for the specified patient.
      Throws:
      PatientNotFoundException - if the patient is not found.
